(2) Issue the receipts on blanks furnished by the cabinet;
(3) Collect the fees due the state;
(4) Distribute the registration plates furnished by the Transportation Cabinet and Department of Vehicle
Regulation and keep a complete public record of all registrations for the[his] county[,] in the clerk's[his]
