(c) The cabinet may[ in its discretion] grant a county clerk an[a reasonable] extension of up to ten (10)
days[time] to file the[his] report and remit all moneys[ not to exceed ten (10) days for any one (1)
report]. The extension[ however] must be requested prior to the end of the seven (7) day period and
